about.summary: Implements univariate polynomial operations in R, including polynomial arithmetic, finding zeros, plotting, and some operations on lists of polynomials.

name: r-polynomf
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.0-3" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-polynomf
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/PolynomF_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/PolynomF/PolynomF_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 89535c4f838c13b970a0b52ac02aa3250f4dc90055e405da7e66cb2f6238f418

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-rcpp
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-rcpp

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('PolynomF')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('PolynomF')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=PolynomF
  license: GPL-2
  summary: Implements univariate polynomial operations in R, including polynomial arithmetic,
    finding zeros, plotting, and some operations on lists of polynomials.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - MathiasHaudgaard
    - FrodePedersen
    - ArneKr
